<item>
            <title>[LU-9242] Applications are failing to complete due to connection loss with OSS servers</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9242</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With my testing of the latest master branch I see jobs failing due to the lose of communication with the OSS servers. I see a reconnect storm but in the end the application error out.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Lustre 2.9.54 running on servers using RHEL7 and using ldiskfs. Client side is Cray SLES11SP4 also running lustre 2.9.54</environment>
